<%= render 'shared/header' %>

<div class="application-page">
  <div class="application-container">
    <div class="application-card">
      <div class="application-header">
        <h1 class="application-title">Speak to a Qualified Adviser</h1>
        <p class="application-subtitle">
          In the United Kingdom, the Equity Preservation Mortgage® is a lifetime mortgage and
          cannot be arranged online.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="application-form">
        <div class="summary-sections">
          <div class="summary-section">
            <h3 class="summary-section-title">Why an adviser is required</h3>
            <p>
              FCA rules require that lifetime mortgages are recommended by a qualified
              equity release adviser, who will assess your circumstances and provide a
              personalised illustration before any application is made.
            </p>
            <p>
              This is a lifetime mortgage. To understand the features and risks, ask for a
              personalised illustration. Your home is used as security. The value of
              investments can go down as well as up. You should seek independent
              financial advice.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="summary-section">
            <h3 class="summary-section-title">What happens next</h3>
            <div class="next-steps-content">
              <div class="next-step-item">
                <div class="step-icon">1</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                  <h4>Contact us</h4>
                  <p>Request a call back and we will connect you with a qualified equity release adviser.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="next-step-item">
                <div class="step-icon">2</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                  <h4>Personalised illustration</h4>
                  <p>Your adviser will prepare a personalised illustration covering income, balances, and estate impact.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="next-step-item">
                <div class="step-icon">3</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                  <h4>Adviser-led application</h4>
                  <p>If the EPM is right for you, your adviser completes the application on your behalf.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-actions">
          <%= link_to "Back to Home", root_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%= render 'shared/footer' %>
